       </p>
   </div>
   
   <div type="textpart" n="G"><head>Section 6</head>
    <p>      
           <lb n="G1"/>madhyamaM
       </p>
       <p>      
           <lb n="G2ff."/><gap reason="lost"/> [list of <foreign>svara</foreign>s probably displayed in columns]
       </p>
   </div>    
    
</div>         
        
