 <div type="commentary">
     <p>This inscription has been erased. What remains of it is its initial blesssing and the headers to series of <foreign>svara</foreign>s, which were probably displayed in columns, like in Kuṭumiyāmalai. See inscription <ref target="DHARMA_INSPallava00022">Pallava 22</ref>, which has comparable headers and the series of <foreign>svara</foreign>s.</p>
 </div>
      	
